Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你來擔任獨奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是中世古同學
